                    <tbody>
                        <row>
                            <entry colspan="3" spanname="SPAN1">
                                <warning>
                                    <para>To avoid serious personal injury, possible death, or damage to the engine or
                                        vehicle, always disconnect main negative battery cable first. Always connect the
                                        main negative battery cable last.
                                    </para>
                                </warning>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry colspan="3" spanname="SPAN1">
                                <para>
                                    <emph type="bold">Connector Voltage Checks</emph>
                                    (Disconnect sensor from harness and turn ignition key ON.)
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry colname="col1">
                                <para>Test Point</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="col2">
                                <para>Spec</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="col3">
                                <para>Comments</para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry colname="col1">
                                <para>A to gnd</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="col2">
                                <para>0V</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="col3">
                                <para>Signal ground (no voltage expected) if voltage is present, check for short to B+
                                    or V
                                    <subscript>REF</subscript>.
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry colname="col1">
                                <para>B to gnd</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="col2">
                                <para>5V &#177;0.5</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="col3">
                                <para>If voltage is not to spec, V
                                    <subscript>REF</subscript>
                                    is open or shorted to ground.
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry colname="col1">
                                <para>C to gnd</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="col2">
                                <para>&#60;0.25</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="col3">
                                <para>If voltage >0.25V, signal ground wire is shorted to V
                                    <subscript>REF</subscript>
                                    or B+.
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry colspan="3" spanname="SPAN1">
                                <para>
                                    <emph type="bold">Connector Resistance Checks to Chassis Ground</emph>
                                    (Turn ignition key OFF. Disconnect negative battery cable and sensor connector.)
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry colname="col1">
                                <para>A to gnd</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="col2">
                                <para>&#60;5&#x2126;</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="col3">
                                <para>If >5&#x2126;, check for open circuit</para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry colname="col1">
                                <para>B to gnd</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="col2">
                                <para>>500&#x2126;</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="col3">
                                <para>If &#60;500&#x2126;, check for short to ground</para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry colname="col1">
                                <para>C to gnd</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="col2">
                                <para>>1k&#x2126;</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="col3">
                                <para>If &#60;1k&#x2126;, check for short to ground</para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry colspan="3" spanname="SPAN1">
                                <para>
                                    <emph type="bold">Harness Resistance Checks</emph>
                                    (Install breakout box on engine harness only.)
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry colname="col1">
                                <para>X1-6 to A</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="col2">
                                <para>&#60;5&#x2126;</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="col3">
                                <para>If >5&#x2126;, check for open ground wire</para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry colname="col1">
                                <para>X1-14 to B</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="col2">
                                <para>&#60;5&#x2126;</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="col3">
                                <para>If >5&#x2126;, check for open V
                                    <subscript>REF</subscript>
                                    wire
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry colname="col1">
                                <para>X2-7 to C</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="col2">
                                <para>&#60;5&#x2126;</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="col3">
                                <para>If >5&#x2126;, check for open signal wire</para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                    </tbody>
                </tgroup>
            </table>
